'''Tarson''' was a first name or a surname shared by:
*[[Tarson Kestrel]], a [[Spice/Legends|spice]] raider during the [[Post-Imperial era/Legends|post-Imperial era]].
*[[Ved Tarson]], a resistance fighter against the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].
*[[Wyl Tarson]], a [[Spy/Legends|spy]] for the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] and Ved Tarson's younger brother.

